overview.en: The Uniex distributed exchange aims to create a chain based trading platform based on a Turing chain to achieve distributed storage of cold node account assets, which effectively improves platform security and excellent user experience.
overview.zh: Uniex分布式交易所旨在打造基于图灵公链的链上交易平台，实现了分布式的冷节点账户资产存储，该系统有效提升了平台安全性以及优秀的用户体验
